				<h3>Background</h3>

				<p>The University of Texas <a href="http://www.mdanderson.org/" target="_blank">MD Anderson Cancer Center</a> is one of the premier cancer treatment centers in the world. Their mission is to eliminate cancer in Texas, the nation, and the world through outstanding programs that integrate patient care, research and prevention, and through education for undergraduate and graduate students, trainees, professionals, employees and the public.</p>
				<p>This was a grant-funded project to develop a virtual environment to train health professionals how to help their patients quit smoking.</p>
