				<h3>Design</h3>

				<p>Subject matter experts at MD Anderson provided us scripts of multiple patient/physician scenarios that provided the basis for the instructional content and user interactions.</p>
				<p>After discussing different user interaction models, we worked with a designer to create wireframes and mockups so that the MD Anderson staff could provide feedback and approve a final design.</p>
			</div>
